text: Vladimír Stibořík (28 July 1927 - 12 December 2014) was a Czech sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Czech male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Czechoslovakia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bruntál District
